  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>A breakfast buffet is available each morning with a selection of pastries, cold meats, cheeses, bread and fresh fruit and juices. Some hot options are also available, including bacon and scrambled eggs. </p>
<p><strong>La Terrazza Restaurant</strong> has a fantastic setting on the lake and offers regional dishes as well as a decent wine list. If you decide to have lunch here you may be able to get a table right on the lake (payable locally).</p>
<p><strong>The Lounge Bar &amp; Pizzeria</strong> is a relaxing space where you can enjoy some delicious cocktails, drinks, snacks and pizzas. At the weekends there's often live music (June onwards). The bar is open from 9am to 11pm (payable locally).</p>]]></cateringDescription>
